    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo自动填充注解"><a href="#hexo自动填充注解" class="headerlink" title="hexo自动填充注解"></a>hexo自动填充注解</h1><p>之前用的阿里云服务器+typecho搭建的博客，但是服务器要续费，和域名等问题，还是让我放弃了。于是使用github来搭建服务器，毕竟很可能我会一直使用我的github账号，并且自带域名。但是hexo要自己写注解来指定文章和分类，就很烦。于是利用chatgpt,和自己的更改写了下面一个脚本进行自动添加注解。</p><figure class="highlight livecodeserver"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs livecodeserver">import os<br>import <span class="hljs-built_in">random</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 定义函数，用于获取相对路径中的目录列表</span><br>def get_categories(rel_path):<br>    categories = []<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> True:<br>        rel_path, tail = os.path.<span class="hljs-built_in">split</span>(rel_path)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> tail:<br>            categories.insert(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, tail)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> rel_path:<br>                categories.insert(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, rel_path)<br>            break<br>    <span class="hljs-literal">return</span> categories<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 定义函数，用于处理一个 md 文件</span><br>def process_md_file(filepath, out_dir):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(filepath, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;r&quot;</span>, encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> infile:<br>        content = infile.<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>()<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 获取相对路径</span><br>    rel_path = os.path.relpath(filepath, os.getcwd())<br>    rel_dir, filename = os.path.<span class="hljs-built_in">split</span>(rel_path)<br>    rel_dir = os.path.normpath(rel_dir)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 获取目录列表</span><br>    categories = get_categories(rel_dir)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 构建输出文件路径</span><br>    out_filepath = os.path.join(out_dir, filename)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">#创建随机数，来实现文章封面文章随机</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">num</span>=<span class="hljs-built_in">random</span>.randint(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 构建 YAML 头部</span><br>    yaml_header = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;---\n&quot;</span><br>    yaml_header += f<span class="hljs-string">&quot;title: &#123;filename[:-3]&#125;\n&quot;</span><br>    yaml_header += <span class="hljs-string">&quot;categories:\n&quot;</span><br>    yaml_header += f<span class="hljs-string">&quot;- &#123;categories&#125;\n&quot;</span><br>    yaml_header += f<span class="hljs-string">&quot;index_img: /img/&#123;num&#125;.jpg\n&quot;</span><br>    yaml_header += <span class="hljs-string">&quot;---\n&quot;</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 写入到输出文件中</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(out_filepath, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;w&quot;</span>, encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> outfile:<br>       <span class="hljs-comment"># print(outfile)</span><br>        outfile.<span class="hljs-built_in">write</span>(yaml_header)<br>        outfile.<span class="hljs-built_in">write</span>(content)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 定义函数，用于处理一个目录</span><br>def process_dir(dirname, out_dir):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> root, dirs, <span class="hljs-built_in">files</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> os.walk(dirname):<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">file</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">files</span>:<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">file</span>.endswith(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.md&quot;</span>):<br>                print(<span class="hljs-built_in">file</span>)<br>                filepath = os.path.join(root, <span class="hljs-built_in">file</span>)<br>                process_md_file(filepath, out_dir)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 调用函数，处理page目录下的所有 md 文件,保存到_posts目录</span><br>process_dir(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;page&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;_posts&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
